{
  "stem": "8892.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you look around and you're seeing, you know, and Israel happened, and what happened in there, but we still have to survive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is-- I always thought about it, this is, why me?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, this is another thing we never went through it, that for a long time we walked around, all the survivors, guilty.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why life?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I'm thinking back, that it had to be a God watching over us, because those things, those little experiences, just what I gave you now, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest of it-- to survive, to work in this condition, and being hungry and still survive, there had to be somebody bigger than us watching us because normally nobody would survive those things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So why was that me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All I know is that when my sister died, this one rabbi I shortly mentioned to you, he came in and he figured out the date for my yahrzeit-- the memorial day-- in Hebrew for me, and he says, Eva, you must live.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There has got to be a purpose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You will be-- you are young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're going to marry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You'll have a family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I think back, that really from that, I have six grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And just a single kid left in a world, somebody was watching over us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[CRYING] But why was it written that it had to be just only me and my two other brothers?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my brother, poor guy, he was very young when he died in here in Detroit in leukemia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's no answer for that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Is there anything else that you would like to say before we bring  in your family?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it's enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
